name: Ys vs. Sora no Kiseki: Alternative Saga
name_original: Ys vs. Sora no Kiseki: Alternative Saga
description:
Ys vs. Sora no Kiseki: Alternative Saga is an action game. It came out on 09-11-2011. The game is rated as "Exceptional" on RAWG.
Ys vs. Sora no Kiseki: Alternative Saga is available on PSP.
It was scored by Hayato Sonoda, Masanori Osaki, Saki Momiyama and Takahiro Unisuga.
